<q-layout>
  <q-header class="bg-grey-2 text-black">
    <q-toolbar>
      <q-btn
        flat
        dense
        round
        @click="leftDrawerOpen = !leftDrawerOpen"
        aria-label="Menu"
        icon="mdi-menu"
      />

      <q-toolbar-title>
        Gantt Elastic demo
      </q-toolbar-title>
    </q-toolbar>
  </q-header>

  <q-drawer v-model="leftDrawerOpen" bordered content-class="bg-grey-2">
    <q-list>
      <q-item clickable @click="$router.push('/')">
        <q-item-section avatar>
          <q-icon name="mdi-code-tags" />
        </q-item-section>
        <q-item-section>
          <q-item-label>Demo</q-item-label>
        </q-item-section>
      </q-item>
      <q-item clickable @click="$router.push('/info')">
        <q-item-section avatar>
          <q-icon name="mdi-file-document-box-multiple" />
        </q-item-section>
        <q-item-section>
          <q-item-label>Documentation</q-item-label>
        </q-item-section>
      </q-item>
    </q-list>
  </q-drawer>

  <q-page-container>
    <router-view />
  </q-page-container>
</q-layout>
